r           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 11\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 11\n| Title               = Decepto the Great\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|10|13}}\n| ShortSummary        = A magician, Decepto the Great, comes to town, planning on stealing from the school kids.\n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 12\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 12\n| Title               = The Thing's the Play\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|10|13}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 13\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 13\n| Title               = Double Trouble for the Thing\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|10|20}}\n| ShortSummary        = An evil scientist creates a robot Thing to rob the citizens and make them think The Thing has gone bad.\n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 14\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 14\n| Title               = To Thing or Not to Thing\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|10|20}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 15\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 15\n| Title               = The Big Bike Race\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|10|27}}\n| ShortSummary        = Benjy enters a cross country bike race because the winner gets to escort the Race Queen to the dance.\n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 16\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 16\n| Title               = The Thing and the Treasure Hunt\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|10|27}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 17\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 17\n| Title               = Out to Launch\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|11|3}}\n| ShortSummary        = Benjy and his friends are going to a ship launching but the world's greatest demolition